Kizz Daniel has responded to a lady who demanded he addressed the rumour about him being close-fisted. The lady, identified as Chelsea, claimed she stumbled on a rumour that Vado was stingy and asked him to dispel it by sending her N100,000.   Buhari celebrates Abdulsalami Abubakar at 80     APC Yobe aggrieved aspirants threaten court action     Owo killings: Oyo govt declares 3-day of mourning   “Vado I hear rumours that you are stingy. Kindly prove them wrong and dash me 100k,” she tweeted. Responding, the “Buga” hit maker insisted he had nothing to prove as he affirmed that he was truly stingy. “No worry, I am stingy. I prove nothing wrong,” Kizz Daniel wrote.